1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 c5 3. d5 e6 4. Nc3 exd5 5. cxd5 d6 6. Nf3 g6 7. Bf4 Bg7 { This is one of the two mainlines of the Modern Benoni. As always, please try to understand the ideas and you don't need to memorize moves. } *[Event "EU-ch 9th"]
