1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 e6 3. Nf3 c5 4. d5 exd5 5. cxd5 d6 6. Nc3 g6 7. h3 Bg7 8. Bf4 O-O 9. e3 Na6 10. Bxa6 bxa6 11. Rc1 Rb8 12. b3 a5 13. O-O Rb4 ( 13... Ba6 14. Re1 { planning e4-e5. } 14... h6 15. e4 Re8 16. Qd2 g5 17. Bh2 c4 18. Nd4 { planning Nf5. White is clearly better. } ) 14. Re1 Nh5 ( 14... Re8 15. a3 { planning e4 next } 15... Rb8 16. e4 $14 { White has a good advantage. } ) 15. Bh2 f5 16. a3 Rb7 17. e4 Bxc3 ( 17... f4 { would be a good move but unfortunately, Black does not control the center. } 18. e5 { creating a passed pawn, White is much better. } ) 18. Rxc3 fxe4 19. Nd2 Nf6 20. Nxe4 Nxe4 21. Rxe4 Bf5 22. Re1 a4 23. bxa4 Rb1 24. Rc1 Rb2 25. Bg3 Qf6 26. Re2 Bd7 $4 27. Be5 1-0[Event "Chessable Masters Div 3 L"]
