1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 e6 3. Nc3 Bb4 4. e3 O-O 5. Bd3 d5 6. a3 Bxc3+ 7. bxc3 dxc4 8. Bxc4 c5 9. Ne2 Qc7 10. Bd3 e5 11. dxe5 $1 Qxe5 12. O-O b6 13. Qc2 Rd8 ( 13... Bb7 14. Ng3 Nbd7 15. Bb2 $16 Qe7 16. c4 Ne5 17. Be2 $16 { White's dark-squared bishop is especcially strong. } ) 14. Bb2 $16 Bb7 ( 14... Qd5 { just doesn't work: } 15. Rad1 $18 ) 15. c4 Qg5 16. Ng3 $18 { Just like that, White is winning! He is ready to push f4 and e4 and steamroll Black's position! } 16... Nbd7 17. f4 Qg4 18. e4 Nf8 19. Bxf6 gxf6 20. Nf5 Kh8 21. Qc3 Nd7 22. Rf2 Bc6 23. Re1 Re8 24. Bc2 Re6 25. Re3 Rg8 26. Rg3 Qh5 27. Rh3 Qg4 28. Rh4 Qg6 29. Rh6 { Black loses the queen. } 1-0[Event "Titled Tuesday intern op 21st Jun Early"]
