1. d4 e6 2. c4 Nf6 3. Nc3 Bb4 4. a3 ( 4. e3 { This would be our move order to get to the same position } 4... O-O 5. Bd3 d5 6. a3 Bxc3+ 7. bxc3 c5 ( 7... Nbd7 8. cxd5 exd5 9. Ne2 $14 ) 8. cxd5 exd5 9. Ne2 b6 ( 9... Nc6 10. O-O b6 11. Ng3 Bb7 12. f3 Re8 13. Ra2 Rc8 14. Raf2 $16 ) 10. O-O Ba6 11. Bxa6 ( 11. Ng3 ) 11... Nxa6 12. Qd3 Nc7 13. dxc5 bxc5 14. c4 dxc4 15. Qxc4 Ne6 16. Bb2 $14 ) 4... Bxc3+ 5. bxc3 b6 6. f3 d5 7. cxd5 exd5 8. e3 O-O 9. Bd3 c5 10. Ne2 Ba6 11. Bxa6 Nxa6 12. O-O Nc7 13. Ng3 Nb5 14. Qd3 c4 $2 { after this, white's center is left without any pressure..and white is almost winning already !! } 15. Qc2 Re8 16. Re1 Nd6 17. e4 h6 18. e5 Nb7 19. Nf5 Nd7 20. f4 Nf8 21. Re3 Re6 22. Rh3 Rg6 23. Be3 b5 24. Rf1 Qd7 25. Ng3 Rc6 26. f5 f6 27. exf6 Rxf6 28. Bf4 Nh7 29. Be5 Rf7 30. Nh5 Nf6 31. Bxf6 gxf6 32. Qd2 Nd6 33. Qxh6 Ne4 34. Rf4 Rh7 35. Qg6+ Kh8 36. Nxf6 Nxf6 37. Qxf6+ Qg7 38. Rxh7+ Kxh7 39. Rh4+ Kg8 40. Qe6+ Kf8 41. f6 Qg8 42. Qe7# 1-0[Event "38th Greek Team Championship"]
