1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 e6 3. Nc3 Bb4 4. e3 c5 ( 4... b6 5. Ne2 c5 { is the alternative move order. } ) 5. Ne2 b6 6. a3 Ba5 7. Rb1 Na6 8. Nf4 Bb7 9. Bd3 O-O 10. O-O Bxc3 11. bxc3 Be4 12. Bxe4 ( 12. f3 $1 { is better, not allowing the knight to e4. } 12... Bxd3 13. Qxd3 d6 14. e4 Rc8 15. d5 $16 ) 12... Nxe4 13. Qd3 Nd6 $6 ( { Now Black could have played } 13... f5 { and reach a position close to equality. } ) 14. dxc5 $6 { Black gets excellent compensation for the taken pawn. } ( 14. e4 $14 { was more to the point and somewhat problematic for Black. } ) 14... Nb7 $44 { Black was the side pressing from now on, but the game later turned around due to Black delving into unnecessary complications. } 15. cxb6 axb6 16. Rd1 Nac5 17. Qc2 f5 18. Ne2 Na5 19. Rb4 Nc6 20. Nd4 Ne5 21. h3 Rf6 22. f4 Nf7 23. Nb3 Ne4 24. Nd2 Nfd6 25. Nf3 Nb7 26. a4 Nbc5 27. Bd2 d6 28. Be1 h6 29. Bh4 g5 30. fxg5 hxg5 31. Nxg5 Rh6 32. Nxe4 Rxh4 33. Nxc5 bxc5 34. Rb7 Qg5 35. Qf2 Rxa4 36. Rxd6 Ra8 37. Kh2 Re4 38. Rdd7 Qxe3 39. Qxe3 Rxe3 40. Rg7+ Kh8 41. Rh7+ Kg8 42. Rbg7+ Kf8 43. Rc7 Kg8 44. Rhd7 f4 45. Rg7+ Kh8 46. Rh7+ Kg8 47. Rcg7+ Kf8 48. Rf7+ Kg8 49. Rhg7+ Kh8 50. h4 f3 51. h5 fxg2 52. Rh7+ Kg8 53. Rfg7+ Kf8 54. h6 1-0[Event "Catalunya-chT Gp2"]
