1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 e6 3. Nc3 Bb4 4. e3 O-O 5. Bd3 c5 6. Ne2 cxd4 7. exd4 d5 8. cxd5 Nxd5 9. O-O Nc6 10. Nxd5 exd5 11. Nf4 Be7 12. Be3 Bf6 13. Nh5 ( { White can also just develop a rook: } 13. Re1 $16 ) ( { or } 13. Rc1 $16 ) 13... Re8 14. Rc1 Be6 15. Qf3 Be7 $2 { Black runs straight into a winning attack! White carries out a decisive forced king hunt during the course of several next moves! } 16. Nxg7 $1 Kxg7 17. Qh5 Bf6 18. Qh6+ Kg8 19. Bxh7+ Kh8 20. Bf5+ Kg8 21. Qh7+ Kf8 22. Bh6+ Ke7 23. Bxe6 Kxe6 24. Rfe1+ Kd7 25. Qxf7+ Re7 26. Qxd5+ Ke8 27. Qh5+ Kd7 28. Qf5+ Kc7 29. Bf4+ Kb6 30. Qc5+ Ka6 31. Qc4+ Kb6 32. Rxe7 Qxe7 33. d5 Ne5 34. Qb3+ 1-0[Event "Madras Shaastra rapid 4th"]
