1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 e6 3. Nc3 Bb4 4. e3 O-O 5. Bd3 c5 6. Ne2 d5 7. cxd5 cxd4 8. exd4 Nxd5 9. O-O Nc6 10. Nxd5 exd5 11. Nf4 Bd6 12. Re1 Ne7 $6 { Starting a failed attempt at simplification. } 13. Qf3 Bf5 ( 13... Bxf4 14. Bxf4 Bf5 { also doesn't work: } 15. Rxe7 $1 Bxd3 16. Rxb7 $16 ) 14. Nxd5 Bxd3 15. Nxe7+ Bxe7 16. Qxd3 Bf6 17. d5 Qd7 18. Bf4 $5 { White sacrifices the pawn back for activity and achieves a big advantage with the dangerous passed d-pawn. } 18... Bxb2 19. Rab1 Bf6 20. h3 b6 21. Rbc1 Rac8 22. Rxc8 Rxc8 23. d6 h5 24. Qf3 Qa4 25. Re4 Qc6 26. g4 hxg4 27. hxg4 g5 28. Bg3 Kg7 29. Kg2 Qc1 30. Qe3 Qc6 31. Be5 Re8 32. Qxg5+ Kh7 33. Qf5+ Kg8 34. d7 Rxe5 35. Qxe5 Bxe5 36. d8 Kh7 37. h4 Kg8 38. g5 Bg7 39. f5 a5 40. a4 Bf8 41. Kh3 Qc1 42. Kg2 Qc6 43. f3 Qh6 44. Re8 Qd6 45. e4 Qd7 46. Re5 Qd8 47. e3 Qf6 48. g5 Qxg5 49. Rxg5+ Kh7 50. Rd5 Kg6 51. Kf3 Bc5 52. Rf5 f6 53. Ke4 Bb4 54. Kd3 Bc5 55. f3 Bg1 56. Kc4 Kg7 57. Kd5 1-0[Event "Budapest RWE Gas m"]
