{GREAT ENDGAME PLAY I included extensive notes, which the reader is meant to study and consider on his own. They show various ways of playing out the endgame. If you study this and the other two thematic games on your own, your skill in this type of endgame will reach a considerable level and potentially allow you to extract points in your own games.} 1. c4 c5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. d4 cxd4 4. Nxd4 Nf6 5. Nc3 e6 6. Ndb5 Bb4 7. a3 Bxc3+ 8. Nxc3 d5 9. e3 O-O 10. cxd5 exd5 11. Be2 Bf5 12. Nb5 Qb6 13. O-O a6 14. Nd4 Nxd4 15. Qxd4 Qxd4 16. exd4 Rac8 17. Bd1 (17. Be3 h6 18. Rac1 Rxc1 19. Rxc1 Rc8 20. Rxc8+ Bxc8 21. f3 (21. Bf3 $2 Bg4 $1 22. Bxg4 Nxg4 23. h3 Nxe3 (23... Nf6) 24. fxe3 f6 (24... h5) 25. Kf2 Kf7 26. Kf3 Ke6 27. g4 (27. e4 dxe4+ 28. Kxe4 f5+ 29. Ke3 g5 30. Kd3 Kd5 31. b3 (31. Ke3 Kc4) 31... f4 32. Kc3 h5 33. Kd3 Kd6 (33... b5 34. a4 bxa4 $2) 34. Ke4 Ke6 35. d5+ Kd6 36. Kd4 b5 37. a4 bxa4 (37... b4) (37... g4 38. axb5 axb5 39. hxg4 hxg4 40. Ke4) 38. bxa4 g4 39. hxg4 hxg4 40. Ke4 f3 41. gxf3 gxf3 42. Kxf3 Kxd5 43. Ke3 Kc4 44. Kd2 Kb4 45. Kc2 Kxa4 46. Kb2) (27. b3) 27... g6 (27... g5 $4 28. e4 Kd6 29. Ke3 Ke6 30. b4 b5 31. exd5+ Kxd5 32. Kd3 Ke6 33. Ke4) 28. b4 b5 29. Kf4 g5+ 30. Kf3 f5 31. Kg3 (31. gxf5+ Kxf5 32. Kg3 h5 (32... Ke4) (32... Ke4 33. Kg4 Kxe3 34. Kh5 Kxd4 35. Kxh6 Ke3 36. Kxg5 d4) 33. Kf3 g4+ 34. hxg4+ hxg4+ 35. Kg3 Ke4 36. Kxg4 Kxe3) 31... Kf6 32. Kf3 Kg6 33. Kg3 h5 34. Kf3 (34. gxh5+ Kxh5 35. Kg2 Kh4 36. Kh2 g4 37. hxg4 fxg4 38. e4 dxe4 39. d5 Kg5 40. d6 Kf6 41. Kg3 e3) 34... fxg4+ 35. hxg4 hxg4+ (35... h4 $4) 36. Kxg4 Kf6 37. Kg3 Kf5 38. Kf3 g4+ 39. Kg3 Ke4) 21... Be6 (21... h5 22. Kf2 (22. h4)) 22. g4 Nd7 23. h4) 17... Bc2 18. Be3 Bxd1 19. Rfxd1 Rc2 20. Rd2 Rfc8 21. Rxc2 Rxc2 22. Rc1 Rxc1+ 23. Bxc1 Nd7 (23... h5 24. h3 Kh7 25. Kf1 Nd7 26. Ke2 f6 27. g4 g5 28. f3 Kg6 29. Kf2 f5 30. Bd2 (30. Be3 Nf6) 30... fxg4 (30... Nf6 31. Kg3 (31. gxf5+ Kxf5 32. Kg3 (32. Bc3 g4 (32... Nd7 33. Ke3 Nb6 34. b3 Nc8 35. Bd2 Ne7 36. a4 Nc6) 33. hxg4+ hxg4 34. Ke3 Nh7 35. Be1 gxf3 36. Kxf3 Ng5+ 37. Ke3 Kg4) 32... h4+ 33. Kf2 Nh5) 31... fxg4 32. hxg4 hxg4 33. fxg4 Ne4+) 31. fxg4 Nf6 32. Kf3) 24. Kf1 Nf8 (24... Nb8 25. Be3 Nc6 26. Ke2 Kh8 27. Kd3 Kg8 28. Kc3 Kh8 29. b4 b5) 25. Ke2 Ne6 26. Kd3 h5 (26... Kh8 27. Be3 (27. b4 b5) 27... Kg8 28. Kc3 Kh8 29. Kb4 b6 30. f3 Kg8 31. Bf2 Kh8 32. Bg3 (32. Kc3 Nd8) 32... Nxd4 (32... Kg8 33. Bb8 Nxd4 (33... Nd8 34. Bc7 Nc6+ 35. Kc3 b5)) 33. Bf2 Nc6+ 34. Kc3 b5) (26... Kh8) (26... h6 27. g4 g5) 27. Be3 (27. Kc3 Kh7 (27... Nd8 28. Kb4 b6) 28. Kb4 b6 29. g3 Kh8 30. Bf4 Kh7 31. Bb8 Nd8 32. Bc7 Nc6+ 33. Kc3 b5) (27. b4 b5) 27... Kh7 (27... Kh8) 28. f3 Kg6 (28... g5 29. h3 Kg6 30. g4 Nd8 31. Ke2 Ne6 32. Kf2 Nd8 33. Kg2 Ne6 34. Kh2 f5 35. Kg2 Nc7 (35... fxg4 36. fxg4) 36. Bf2 Ne8 37. Be3 Nf6 (37... fxg4 38. fxg4 hxg4 39. hxg4 Nf6 40. Kf3) 38. gxf5+ Kxf5 39. Kf2 Nd7 40. Kg2 Nf8 41. Kf2 Ne6 42. Kg2 Nf4+ 43. Kh2 Nd3 44. b3 Ne1 45. Kg3 Nc2) (28... g5 29. g4 Kg6 30. h3 f5 31. Ke2 Nc7 (31... Nd8 32. Kf2 Nc6 33. Kg2 Na5 34. Bd2 Nc4 35. Bc3 (35. Bc1 b5)) 32. Kf2 Ne8 33. Bc1 (33. Bd2 Nf6 (33... fxg4 34. fxg4 Nf6 35. Kf3 Ne4 36. Be3)) 33... Nf6 34. Kg3) 29. a4 (29. b4 b5 $1) 29... Kf5 30. Ke2 g5 31. Kf2 Nd8 32. Bd2 Kg6 33. Ke3 Ne6 34. Kd3 Kf5 35. Be3 f6 36. Ke2 Kg6 37. Kd3 (37. g4 f5 38. h3 Ng7 39. Kf2 Ne8 40. Kg2 Nf6 41. gxf5+ Kxf5 42. Kf2 g4 (42... Nd7 43. Bd2 Nb6 44. b3 Nd7 45. Be3 Nb8 46. Bd2 Nc6 47. Bc3 Ne7 48. b4 b5 49. axb5 axb5) 43. fxg4+ hxg4 44. hxg4+ Kxg4 45. Bh6 b5 46. axb5 axb5 47. b4 $2 Ne4+ 48. Ke3 Nd6 49. Bf8 Nf5+ 50. Kd3 Kf3 $19) 37... f5 38. Ke2 (38. b4 b5) 38... f4 39. Bf2 Ng7 40. h3 Nf5 41. Kd3 (41. b4 b5) (41. b4 b5 42. axb5 axb5) 41... g4 42. hxg4 hxg4 43. fxg4 (43. Ke2 g3 44. Bg1 Nh4 45. Kf1 Kh7 46. b4 Kg8 47. a5 Kh7 48. Ke2 Nxg2 49. Kd2 Nh4 50. Ke2 Kh8) 43... Nh6 44. Be1 (44. Ke2 Nxg4 45. Kf3 Kf5 46. Bg1 b5 (46... Nf6 47. Bh2 Nh5 48. Bg1 (48. a5 Kg5) 48... Ng7 49. Bf2 Ne6 50. Bg1 Ng5+ 51. Ke2 Ke4 52. Kd2 f3 53. gxf3+ Nxf3+ 54. Kc3 b5 55. axb5 axb5 56. b4) 47. axb5 axb5 48. b4 Nf6 49. Bh2 Nh5 50. Bg1 Ng7 51. Bf2 Ne6 52. Bg1 Ng5+ 53. Ke2 Ke4 54. Bf2 (54. Kd2 f3 55. gxf3+ Kxf3 56. Kd3 Ne6 57. Bh2 Ng5 58. Be5 Ne6 59. Bf6 Nf4+ 60. Kd2 Ke4 61. Bg7 Ne6 62. Kc3 Ke3 63. Bh6+ Nf4 64. Bg5 Ke4 65. Kd2 Ne6 66. Bf6 Nxd4 67. Kc3 Nc6 68. Kb3 Kd3) 54... Ne6) 44... Nxg4 45. Bd2 Kf5 46. Be1 Nf6 47. Bh4 Nh5 48. Be1 Kg4 49. Ke2 Ng3+ 50. Kd3 (50. Bxg3 Kxg3 51. Kf1 b5 52. axb5 axb5 53. b4 f3 54. Kg1 Kf4 (54... Kg4)) 50... Nf5 (50... Ne4 51. b3 f3 52. gxf3+ Kxf3 53. b4 b5 54. axb5 axb5) 51. Bf2 (51. Ke2 Nxd4+ (51... Nh4 52. Kf2 f3 53. gxf3+ Nxf3 54. Bc3 Kf4 55. Ke2 Nh4 (55... Ke4) 56. b4 (56. Bb4) 56... b5 57. axb5 axb5 58. Kd3 Kf3 59. Bd2 Ng6 60. Bg5 Nf4+ 61. Kd2 Ne6 62. Bf6 Ke4 63. Kc3 Ke3 64. Bg7 Nf4 65. Bh6 Ke4 66. Kd2 (66. Bg7 Ne2+) 66... Ne6 67. Bg7 Nxd4)) 51... Nh4 52. a5 (52. b4 b5 53. axb5 axb5) 52... Nxg2 53. Kc3 Kf3 54. Bg1 Ke2 55. Bh2 f3 56. Bg3 Ne3 57. Kb4 Nf5 0-1

