1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 g6 3. Nc3 d5 4. Nf3 Bg7 5. e3 O-O 6. Qb3 { Main tabiya. } 6... c6 { Passive but playable, In these structures ideas matter more than memorizing the lines. So, please study all the games and you don't need to memorize anything. White has two main options a4 & h3, both to wait and not committing anything early on. } *[Event "Hilversum op-A"]
