1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 g6 3. Nc3 d5 4. Nf3 Bg7 5. e3 O-O 6. Qb3 e6 { This is the main line although not many players are aware about it because our chosen line is not really popular. } 7. Be2 { The most simple. We have two ways to play such positions: 1) The agressive one with usual plans of short castle, Ne5, f4, Bd2-Be1-Bh4 at the appropriate moments. 2) A little slower with Bd2 and centralizing pieces. I recommend the former approach but you are welcome to try out everything, so to gain an idea and get comfortable with the lines. } *[Event "Wch Blitz"]
