{We use the same setup against the Old Indian Defence.} 1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 g6 ({We use the same setup against the Old Indian Defence.} 2... d6 3. Nc3 e5 4. Nf3 Nbd7 5. Bg5) 3. Nc3 Bg7 4. Nf3 O-O 5. Bg5 {The so-called Smyslov System - the starting position of our repertoire.} *

[Site "?"]
[Date "2024.02.13"]
[Round "?"]
[White "KING'S INDIAN"]
[Black "THEORETICAL OVERVIEW"]
[Result "*"]
