1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 g6 3. Nc3 Bg7 4. Nf3 O-O 5. Bg5 d6 6. e3 c6 7. Be2 a6 8. O-O b5 9. a3 $5 Nbd7 10. Qc2 ( 10. Nd2 $14 { this appears to be the best..and capture on c4 with the kningt! } 10... bxc4 11. Nxc4 ) ( 10. e4 $14 ) 10... bxc4 11. Bxc4 c5 $13 12. Rfd1 Bb7 13. Rac1 Bxf3 14. gxf3 cxd4 15. Rxd4 $11 { An unclear position with chances for both sides. After a tough fight, Black won. } 15... Nc5 16. Rdd1 a5 17. b4 axb4 18. axb4 Ncd7 19. f4 Rc8 20. Qb3 Rb8 21. Bb5 Kh8 22. Bc6 Nb6 23. Nb5 Nc8 24. Nc3 e6 25. b5 Qb6 26. Qa3 Kg8 27. h3 d5 28. f5 Nh5 29. e4 h6 30. fxe6 fxe6 31. Be3 d4 32. Na4 Qa7 33. Bd2 Nb6 34. Bb4 Qxa4 35. Bxf8 Rxf8 36. Qc5 Nf4 37. Rd2 Qa5 38. Rcd1 Qc3 39. Qxc3 dxc3 40. Rc2 Nc4 41. Kf1 Nxh3 0-1[Event "Bugojno"]
