{ A good effort by myself, against a dangerous and talented opponent! } 1. Nf3 Nf6 2. c4 g6 3. Nc3 Bg7 4. d4 O-O 5. Bg5 c5 6. d5 d6 7. e3 h6 8. Bh4 g5 9. Bg3 Nh5 10. Bd3 Nxg3 ( 10... Na6 $2 11. Nxg5 Nxg3 12. hxg3 hxg5 13. Bh7+ Kh8 14. Qh5 $18 ) ( 10... Bxc3+ $2 11. bxc3 $16 Kg7 $2 12. Nxg5 $1 Nxg3 13. hxg3 hxg5 14. Qh5 $18 ) 11. hxg3 e6 ( 11... Re8 12. O-O $1 ( 12. Nh2 $16 ) 12... Bxc3 13. bxc3 e5 14. dxe6 $1 ( 14. Qc2 ) 14... Bxe6 ( 14... fxe6 15. Nh2 $18 { [%csl Rg8][%cal Yd1h5,Yf2f4] } ) 15. Nh2 ( 15. Rb1 $5 b6 16. Nh2 ( 16. Be4 ) 16... Nd7 17. f4 Nf6 18. e4 Qe7 19. Rb2 ) 15... Nd7 16. f4 $16 ) ( 11... e5 12. e4 $16 { A very instructive move! Now we want to play on the light squares, taking advantage of the move ...g5! If black dares to play ...f5, we take ef5 and establish a piece on e4! } 12... Na6 ( 12... f5 13. exf5 Bxf5 14. Bxf5 Rxf5 15. Ne4 $16 ) 13. Nd2 Nc7 14. Nf1 $3 a6 15. a4 Rb8 16. Ne3 $18 { Black is compeletely lost ! } 16... Bd7 17. Qh5 ( 17. a5 ) 17... b5 18. axb5 axb5 19. cxb5 Nxb5 20. Bxb5 Bxb5 21. Nxb5 Rxb5 22. Ng4 $18 ) 12. Qc2 exd5 ( 12... Na6 13. a3 $16 ) 13. Nxd5 $1 ( 13. cxd5 $2 Nd7 $13 ( 13... f5 ) ) 13... Be6 ( 13... Re8 14. Bh7+ Kf8 15. O-O Nc6 16. Rad1 $16 ) 14. Bh7+ $1 { REMEMBER THIS CHECK! We want to send the black king to the very dangerous h-file! } 14... Kh8 15. Bf5 Bxd5 ( 15... Nc6 16. Bxe6 fxe6 17. Nc3 $16 ( 17. Qg6 $16 ) 17... Kg8 ( 17... Qe7 18. Qg6 $18 ) 18. O-O Qe7 19. Rad1 $16 Nb4 20. Qe2 Bxc3 21. bxc3 Nc6 22. Qd3 $16 ) 16. cxd5 Na6 17. a3 Re8 ( 17... Qf6 18. O-O-O { This appears to be dangerous but Nh2-g4 comes very fast! } 18... b5 19. Nh2 b4 20. Ng4 Qe7 21. Nxh6 $18 ) 18. Rh5 { Threatening to take on g5 and also the maneuver Nh2-g4. } 18... Kg8 ( 18... Qf6 19. O-O-O $16 ) 19. Rd1 $1 ( 19. Nh2 Qa5+ ) ( 19. O-O-O $5 ) 19... b5 ( 19... Qf6 20. Rd2 Nc7 21. Nh2 Re5 ( 21... Qe7 22. Ng4 b5 23. Nxh6+ Bxh6 24. Rxh6 $18 ) 22. Bh7+ Kf8 23. Ng4 $16 ) 20. Nh2 b4 21. Ng4 bxa3 22. bxa3 Kf8 23. Nxh6 Qf6 24. Ng4 Qc3+ 25. Qxc3 Bxc3+ 26. Kf1 ( 26. Ke2 $5 Rab8 27. Rxg5 c4 28. Rh1 $16 ) 26... Rab8 27. Bd3 Nc7 28. Rxg5 Rb3 29. Nh6 $18 { I calculated the game continuation accurately untill the end. } 29... Rxa3 30. Rg8+ Ke7 31. Nf5+ Kf6 ( 31... Kd7 32. Rxe8 Nxe8 33. Bb5+ Kd8 34. Bxe8 Kxe8 35. Nxd6+ $18 ) 32. Rxe8 Nxe8 33. f4 $18 { The black king is caught in a mating net! } 33... c4 34. Bb1 Bb4 ( 34... Rb3 35. g4 Kg6 36. Ke2 $18 ) ( 34... Ng7 35. Nxd6 $18 ) 35. g4 { Black resigned. } ( 35. g4 Ng7 36. g5+ Kg6 37. Nxd6+ Kh5 38. Nxc4 Rc3 39. Bd3 $18 ( 39. Ne5 Rxe3 40. Kf2 Bc5 41. Rh1+ $4 Rh3+ $19 ) ) 1-0[Event "?"]
