{ A nice game by White up to some point! Black, although an experienced player, did not know the Nd2 idea!! } 1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 g6 3. Nc3 Bg7 4. Bg5 d6 5. e3 O-O 6. Nf3 Nbd7 7. Be2 c5 $2 8. d5 ( 8. h3 $5 { Preventing ...h6-g5-Nh5. } ) 8... a6 ( { Best for Black was } 8... h6 9. Bh4 g5 10. Bg3 Nh5 11. Qc2 Nxg3 12. hxg3 Nf6 ( 12... e5 13. Bd3 $16 { White must prevent ...f5. I like this move best. } ( 13. g4 $1 ) ( 13. e4 $1 ) 13... a6 14. Bh7+ Kh8 15. Bf5 ) 13. Rd1 $5 Bd7 14. e4 Qc7 15. Nd2 $14 { [%cal Yf2f4] } ( 15. Nh2 ) ) 9. a4 { White must choose between this and Nd2. } ( 9. Nd2 $14 { is the best move but gives Black the chance to play } 9... b5 ( 9... Rb8 $2 { Black misses his chance. } 10. a4 { Now Black has no counterplay at all. } 10... e6 ( 10... Qc7 11. O-O Ne8 12. e4 $16 ) 11. O-O ( 11. dxe6 fxe6 12. Nde4 $16 ) 11... exd5 12. cxd5 $16 ) 10. cxb5 axb5 11. Bxb5 Ba6 12. Bxa6 Rxa6 13. O-O $14 { Black has some compensation but maybe not quite enough. } ) 9... Qc7 $2 ( { Black misses the last chance for } 9... h6 10. Bh4 g5 11. Bg3 Nh5 12. Qc2 Nxg3 13. hxg3 Nf6 $14 ) 10. Nd2 $16 { Now White has a stable advantage. } 10... Re8 11. O-O e6 12. e4 ( 12. dxe6 $16 ) 12... exd5 13. cxd5 $16 Ne5 14. h3 h6 15. Bh4 ( 15. Bxf6 $5 Bxf6 16. f4 Nd7 17. e5 dxe5 18. f5 e4 19. Ncxe4 $18 ( 19. Ndxe4 $16 ) ) 15... g5 16. Bg3 Ng6 17. Qc2 Nd7 18. Rfe1 Nde5 19. Nd1 Qe7 20. Ne3 Qf6 21. Nf5 Ne7 22. Nxg7 Kxg7 23. Rf1 ( 23. Bxe5 $3 Qxe5 24. Nc4 Qf6 25. Bh5 $1 ( 25. Qc3 $1 Qxc3 26. bxc3 Rd8 27. a5 $18 ) 25... Ng6 26. Bxg6 Qxg6 27. Qc3+ Kh7 28. e5 $18 ) 23... N7g6 24. Nc4 Nxc4 25. Bxc4 Nf4 26. Rfe1 Bd7 27. a5 Re5 28. Rab1 Rae8 29. f3 Qg6 30. Qd2 f5 31. Bxf4 gxf4 32. Bd3 fxe4 33. Bxe4 Qg5 34. Kh1 Kf7 35. b4 c4 36. Rbc1 Bb5 37. g4 fxg3 38. Qxg5 Rxg5 39. Kg2 Kf6 40. h4 Rg7 41. Rh1 Rc7 42. Rh3 Rg8 43. Rxg3 Rxg3+ 44. Kxg3 Ke5 45. Kg4 c3 46. Kh5 Kd4 47. Kxh6 Bd3 48. h5 Bxe4 49. fxe4 Kxe4 50. Kg6 Kxd5 51. h6 Kc4 52. h7 Rxh7 53. Kxh7 d5 54. Kg6 d4 55. Kf5 d3 56. Ke4 d2 57. Rd1 c2 58. Rxd2 c1 59. Rd4+ Kb5 60. Ke5 c3 61. Ke4 cxd4 62. Kxd4 Kxb4 63. Kd5 Kxa5 64. Kc4 Ka4 0-1[Event "Rilton Cup 31st"]
