1. d4 Nf6 2. Nf3 g6 3. c4 Bg7 4. Nc3 O-O 5. Bg5 d6 6. e3 c5 7. d5 b5 8. cxb5 a6 9. Nd2 ( 9. a4 $5 ) 9... h6 10. Bh4 axb5 11. Bxb5 Ba6 12. a4 ( 12. Bxa6 { is also good. } ) 12... Qa5 13. Ra3 $16 { A typical way to protect the rook. } 13... Qb4 14. Bxf6 $1 Bxf6 15. Rb3 Qa5 16. Nc4 Qc7 { Black has been pushed back. White controls everything and is a clear pawn up. } 17. O-O $16 Nd7 18. Bxa6 Bxc3 $2 19. Rb7 $18 1-0[Event "Porec op 12th"]
