1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 g6 3. Nc3 Bg7 4. Nf3 d6 5. Bg5 h6 6. Bh4 O-O 7. e3 c5 8. Be2 ( 8. d5 $1 ) 8... Nc6 $2 ( 8... cxd4 $1 ) 9. O-O ( 9. d5 $16 ) 9... g5 10. Bg3 Nh5 11. d5 $1 Na5 12. Nd2 Nxg3 13. hxg3 $16 { Now, even the knight on a5 is misplaced. However, we should rather not gamble by waiting for ...Nc6 but push d5! right away after ...c5! } 13... e6 14. g4 exd5 15. Nxd5 Bxb2 16. Rb1 Bg7 17. Bd3 Nc6 18. Bf5 b6 19. Ne4 Ne5 20. Qe2 Ba6 21. Rfc1 Re8 22. g3 Nc6 23. Kg2 Bb7 24. Kh2 Nd4 25. exd4 Bxd4 26. Rd1 Kg7 27. Rd3 Bxd5 28. cxd5 Be5 29. Kg2 a6 30. a4 Rb8 31. Rdb3 a5 32. Qa6 Qc7 33. Rxb6 c4 34. Rc6 Qe7 35. Rxb8 Rxb8 36. Qxc4 Rb2 37. Rc7 Qf8 38. Be6 1-0[Event "?"]
