1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 g6 3. Nc3 Bg7 4. Bg5 O-O 5. e3 c5 6. d5 d6 7. Bd3 $5 ( 7. Nf3 ) 7... h6 8. Bh4 a6 9. a4 Nbd7 $2 ( 9... e6 10. Nf3 exd5 11. cxd5 Bg4 $1 { with a totally acceptable version of the Benoni for Black. } ) 10. f4 $16 ( { or } 10. Nf3 $16 { , for example } 10... Ng4 11. O-O Nge5 12. Nxe5 Nxe5 13. f4 $1 ( 13. Be2 $16 ) 13... Nxd3 14. Qxd3 Qc7 ( 14... f5 15. h3 Bd7 16. Rae1 $16 { [%cal Ye3e4] } ) 15. e4 Re8 16. f5 g5 17. Bg3 $16 ) 10... e6 11. dxe6 fxe6 12. Bxg6 Nb6 13. b3 d5 14. a5 Nbd7 15. cxd5 e5 16. f5 e4 17. Nge2 Qe7 18. O-O Ne5 19. Nf4 Neg4 20. Qxg4 Nxg4 21. Bxe7 Bxc3 22. Bxf8 Bxa1 23. Bxc5 Be5 24. h3 Nf6 25. Rd1 Bxf4 26. exf4 Bd7 27. b4 Re8 28. Kf2 Bb5 29. Ke3 Bc4 30. d6 Nd5+ 31. Rxd5 Bxd5 32. d7 Rd8 33. Be8 Bc6 34. Bb6 Rxd7 35. Bxd7 Bxd7 36. g4 Bc6 37. h4 Kf7 38. g5 hxg5 39. fxg5 Bd5 40. Kf4 Bc6 41. g6+ Kf6 42. Bd4+ Ke7 43. h5 Be8 44. h6 1-0[Event "ARG-ch"]
