1. d4 d6 2. c4 e5 3. Nf3 Nd7 4. Nc3 Ngf6 5. Bg5 h6 6. Bh4 c6 7. e3 Be7 8. Be2 O-O 9. O-O Re8 10. Qc2 Qc7 11. dxe5 ( 11. h3 $3 { The same plan as in the Smyslov King's Indian - it is working perfectly here as well...Bh4-h3!-Bg3! } 11... Bf8 12. Bg3 $16 ) 11... dxe5 12. Nd2 Nf8 13. a3 Ng6 14. Bg3 Bg4 15. Bd3 Nf8 16. h3 Be6 17. b4 a6 18. c5 Rad8 19. Nc4 Bxc4 20. Bxc4 Rd7 21. Rad1 Red8 22. Qb3 Kh8 23. Bxf7 Rxd1 24. Rxd1 Rxd1+ 25. Nxd1 Ne4 26. Bh2 Qd8 27. Bxe5 Qd2 28. f3 Ng5 29. Bc3 Qe2 30. Bc4 Nxh3+ 31. Kh2 1-0

